{"tid":592441,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣後生仔港式殺女友,又一反映男朋友都係揀大年紀好","createTime":"2018-03-14T08:11:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-14T08:13:53.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3d936afdbc6784673f9c3b297f21ce2370e7b1d0","tid":592441,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:11:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180314/57945353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F57945353&d=GCF33%2Fs%2F6JqYT7mrWSgHcf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=781f6bae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180314%2F57945353&h=76b6d37a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180314/57945353</a><br />\n<br />\n20歲少女潘曉穎（20歲）與<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">19歲</span>姓陳男友上月共赴台灣旅行，卻慘遭殺害棄屍荒郊。潘曉穎生前曾就修讀香港專業教育學院(IVE)高級文憑課程，但已退學，學院發言人對事件深感難過，會向有需要的學生提供支援和輔導。"},{"pid":"1652eef521bbf646148908bbbbfa5d66b8d31276","tid":592441,"uid":92340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-14T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"未睇內容就學人出POST，仲出理心得，好撚野"}]}